details.n: May I Ask for One Final Thing?

ratings.en: Akutoku Kizoku (Butayarou-tachi) o Omouzonbun Bokoboko ni Shite Sukatto Shite mo Yoroshii Deshou ka

Chanto Hanashiai de Kaiketsu Shiyou to Omoi Mashita ga, Yahari Bonbon Boko Joui Kizoku o Nagutte mo Yoroshii Deshou ka
Kobushi no Omoibito (Sandobaggu) ni Aini mo Yoroshii Deshou ka
